node.text: Wanted to remind you to never take a day for granted. That you are so worthy of this life and strong enough to live it. Our physical bodies may have expiration dates but our souls do not!! 🤍💭 live your life! Do what makes you happy! Sorry for the tears but when I feel these things I know in my heart it’s because I’m meant to share them... I love you. Keep going. Keep fighting. Keep the faith.
